[
    {
        "text": "Hello. Welcome to Michael's Better Business English.",
        "startTime": 415,
        "endTime": 3254,
        "slowStartTime": 773,
        "slowEndTime": 5106
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at how to lead a meeting.",
        "startTime": 3786,
        "endTime": 6262,
        "slowStartTime": 5829,
        "slowEndTime": 9618
    },
    {
        "text": "Now of course, this can be difficult in Japanese as well as in English.",
        "startTime": 6973,
        "endTime": 10686,
        "slowStartTime": 10609,
        "slowEndTime": 16254
    },
    {
        "text": "There are three key things you need to do to lead a meeting successfully.",
        "startTime": 11407,
        "endTime": 14837,
        "slowStartTime": 17260,
        "slowEndTime": 22481
    },
    {
        "text": "First, keep the meeting on topic.",
        "startTime": 15596,
        "endTime": 18320,
        "slowStartTime": 23544,
        "slowEndTime": 27705
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, shorten overlong discussions.",
        "startTime": 19137,
        "endTime": 22323,
        "slowStartTime": 28855,
        "slowEndTime": 33710
    },
    {
        "text": "Third, resolve conflict.",
        "startTime": 22890,
        "endTime": 25421,
        "slowStartTime": 34485,
        "slowEndTime": 38356
    },
    {
        "text": "How can you do this?",
        "startTime": 26309,
        "endTime": 27310,
        "slowStartTime": 39614,
        "slowEndTime": 41190
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, for keeping the meeting on topic, it's very useful to have a written agenda.",
        "startTime": 27897,
        "endTime": 33160,
        "slowStartTime": 41996,
        "slowEndTime": 49965
    },
    {
        "text": "Then in the meeting, you can refer to the agenda and stop people from getting sidetracked,...",
        "startTime": 33938,
        "endTime": 39303,
        "slowStartTime": 51057,
        "slowEndTime": 59179
    },
    {
        "text": "...going off-topic.",
        "startTime": 39596,
        "endTime": 40749,
        "slowStartTime": 59544,
        "slowEndTime": 61348
    },
    {
        "text": "We often use that expression, \"Let's not get sidetracked.\" in a meeting...",
        "startTime": 41504,
        "endTime": 45459,
        "slowStartTime": 62406,
        "slowEndTime": 68414
    },
    {
        "text": "...to keep the meeting on topic.",
        "startTime": 45833,
        "endTime": 47357,
        "slowStartTime": 68900,
        "slowEndTime": 71261
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, shorten overlong discussions.",
        "startTime": 48659,
        "endTime": 51129,
        "slowStartTime": 73139,
        "slowEndTime": 76918
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, it's very useful to refer to specific times,...",
        "startTime": 51811,
        "endTime": 55117,
        "slowStartTime": 77866,
        "slowEndTime": 82901
    },
    {
        "text": "...such as the end time of the meeting or deadline,...",
        "startTime": 55435,
        "endTime": 58457,
        "slowStartTime": 83303,
        "slowEndTime": 87911
    },
    {
        "text": "...to help people keep focused and avoid wasting time.",
        "startTime": 58824,
        "endTime": 61829,
        "slowStartTime": 88386,
        "slowEndTime": 92969
    },
    {
        "text": "Third, to resolve conflict.",
        "startTime": 63229,
        "endTime": 65158,
        "slowStartTime": 94993,
        "slowEndTime": 97962
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, you should stay calm, be neutral and move the discussion on.",
        "startTime": 65708,
        "endTime": 70005,
        "slowStartTime": 98712,
        "slowEndTime": 105233
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe move on to a less controversial topic or a different item on the agenda,...",
        "startTime": 70648,
        "endTime": 75825,
        "slowStartTime": 106122,
        "slowEndTime": 113963
    },
    {
        "text": "...before going back to that original item.",
        "startTime": 76228,
        "endTime": 78475,
        "slowStartTime": 114492,
        "slowEndTime": 117937
    },
    {
        "text": "Or even take a break.",
        "startTime": 79753,
        "endTime": 81027,
        "slowStartTime": 119779,
        "slowEndTime": 121765
    },
    {
        "text": "That can let people calm down and relax.",
        "startTime": 81490,
        "endTime": 83779,
        "slowStartTime": 122385,
        "slowEndTime": 125894
    },
    {
        "text": "So, use these techniques to lead a meeting successfully.",
        "startTime": 84641,
        "endTime": 88541,
        "slowStartTime": 127111,
        "slowEndTime": 133037
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you very much.",
        "startTime": 89321,
        "endTime": 90245,
        "slowStartTime": 134132,
        "slowEndTime": 135592
    }
]